<h3>The Music Editor</h3>

<p>Also known as <b>Gauntlet</b>, OMG's built-in editor puts 
<i>you</i> in control of the musical puzzle pieces.</p>

<p>In a landscape window, the editor shows two <b>panels</b>, the <b>main panel</b> to the left
    and a <b>detail panel</b> to the right. In a portrait window (like a mobile device), 
    the editor shows one <b>panel</b> at a time, along with a <b>Back</b> button to return to the <b>main panel</b>.
    </p>

<p>The <b>Panels</b> are:</p>

<ul>
<li>Main</li>
<li>User</li>
<li>Song</li>
<li>Section</li>
<li>Save</li>
<li>Beats</li>
<li>Key</li>
<li>Chord Progression</li>
<li>Vertical Surface</li>
<li>Sequencer Surface</li>
<li>Part Options</li>
<li>Song Options</li>
<li>Add Part</li>
<li>Mix</li>
<li>Live</li>
</ul>
